data.description: Located in the desirable 55+ community of Panorama Village this home is on one of the larger lots at 6,534 SF and includes a 2-car garage.  The 1,483 SF interior includes (2) spacious bedrooms - the master suite with its own bath and the 2nd bedroom has its own direct entry to the 2nd or guest bath.  There is a den/office/crafts room off the kitchen and an enclosed sunroom at the back of the home that provides lots of versatility with living space. The covered patio and spacious back yard give this home the perfect mix of venues for entertaining and bbq'ing.  The HOA is a bargain at $120.00 a month and includes a 9-hole-3 par golf course, swimming pool, spas, gym, shuffleboard, library, pool room, clubhouse and 2 dog parks.
